{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, this article only summarizes and discusses each method from the perspective of implementation.",
    "Huang et al. (2020) proposed a global registration method of three-dimensional point cloud based on decoder, FMR.",
    "The coordinate information input point cloud is restored by decoder to achieve the effect of eliminating redundancy and information loss of global features extracted from input point cloud.",
    "Registration by global features does not require RANSAC, so it has a greater advantage in speed than removing mismatched points.",
    "Lu et al. (2019a) proposed a simple network based on spatial and channel attention called SCANet."
  ]
}